                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-11-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">卜正民的經典作，其實就是講故事給你聽，不過裡面藏著些分析還是蠻到位的…同時感謝秀麗姐姐在哈佛當學生給老闆幹活翻譯了這書</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="995581962">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-995581962" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-995581962" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="995581962">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/ruawas/">七七|不言</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很好看的学术著作，能够满足各种对历史的期待，档案或八卦，经验或教训。和《蒙元》一样，力图从历史书的真空中将真实鲜活的东西解放出来。数据很有说服力，论证也非常精当，不愧当年列文森</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="301618166">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-301618166" class="vote-count">0</span>
